# Data Privacy Notice
## Geospatial Road Risk Intelligence Analytics

---

## Notice

Sample data was formally requested from the relevant authorities authorities for portfolio development purposes under a consulting engagement with Ryan Watson Consulting Pty Ltd.

The dataset reflects the real structure, field definitions and inspection methodology of the LiDAR pavement survey conducted across a Queensland urban road network.

---

## What This Repository Contains

- Data dictionary documenting all field names, data types and definitions
- Sample data structure file with fictional values matching the real schema
- Full analytical methodology and DAX implementation
- Power BI report file without underlying dataset

## What This Repository Does Not Contain

- Raw inspection data from the council survey
- GPS coordinates of actual road segments
- Council-identifying information
- Any data that could identify individual properties or residents

